Change logic to use autoloader. Autoloader put in assets folder.

Create pages folder which will contain content for pages (for examples index_content.php)

Meta class put in Web folder and Web namespace

In class Header create method renderHeader which will generate header with title, links and meta tags. Leave constructor and renderHeader methods, delete other methods in Header class.

In class Body create method getContent which will require content page for page (for example index_content.php for index.php page)

In class Footer create renderFooter which will render footer. Delete other methods except constructor and renderFooter.

Create pages aboutus.php and contact.php.

In config.php file add values for these pages where is it necessary.




